videos.headline: Maryland scores 81-yd TD to open game
videos.description: The Terrapins strike first against the Buckeyes with an 81-yard touchdown by RB Anthony McFarland.

videos.headline: Maryland recovers kickoff after odd bounce
videos.description: Ohio State failed to jump on a bouncing kickoff and Maryland takes over in great position.

videos.headline: Maryland jumps ahead 14-3 vs. Ohio State
videos.description: Maryland RB Anthony McFarland runs for another long touchdown against Ohio State.

videos.headline: Haskins throws 68-yard TD for Buckeyes
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins hits Terry McLaurin on a 68-yard touchdown pass to close the gap with Maryland to 17-10

videos.headline: Maryland answers Ohio State with TD
videos.description: The Terrapins find the end zone on a 16-yard rushing score to go up 24-10 over the Buckeyes.

videos.headline: Dobbins reaches over pile for TD
videos.description: Ohio State RB J.K. Dobbins reaches over the pile to score a 1-yard touchdown to cut Maryland's lead to 24-17.

videos.headline: Terps recover Buckeyes' goal-line fumble
videos.description: Maryland's defense recovers J.K. Dobbins' fumble at the goal line.

videos.headline: 4th-down troubles enrage Meyer
videos.description: Urban Meyer unleashes his emotions and throws his headset as Ohio State fails to capitalize on fourth-down plays on both sides of the ball.

videos.headline: Pick-six helps Terps pad lead on Buckeyes
videos.description: Maryland's defense takes Dwayne Haskins' intercepted pass to the house.

videos.headline: Haskins keeps it for 2-yd TD
videos.description: Ohio State QB Dwayne Haskins fakes the handoff and finds the end zone for another Ohio State score.

videos.headline: Game-tying TD ties Haskins for Buckeyes' TD record
videos.description: QB Dwayne Haskins finds K.J. Hill on a six-yard score to even the game, and tie J.T. Barrett's record with 35 Ohio State touchdowns.

videos.headline: Terps' TD upheld after review
videos.description: Ohio State challenges a catch that was ruled down at the 1, but officials overturn the call and rule it a Maryland touchdown.

videos.headline: Buckeyes tie it up on Haskins' 2nd rushing score
videos.description: Buckeyes QB Dwayne Haskins' 1-yard score ties the game with the Terrapins in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Deep pass gets Maryland to the 1-yard line
videos.description: Maryland's Tyrell Pigrome finds Darryl Jones on a 60-yard pass that was originally ruled a touchdown.

videos.headline: Maryland recovers own fumble for go-ahead TD
videos.description: Anthony McFarland fumbles on third down but Maryland teammate Mary Chigoziem Okonkwo recovers the ball for the go-ahead score.

videos.headline: Haskins finds Victor for tying TD in final minute
videos.description: Ohio State QB Dwayne Haskins hits Binjimen Victor on a 3-yard touchdown pass to tie the game late in regulation.

videos.headline: Haskins dives for overtime TD
videos.description: Dwyane Haskins strikes first for Ohio State in OT with a five-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Maryland misses on 2-point conversion, Buckeyes survive
videos.description: Maryland loses to Ohio State in overtime after failing to complete a two-point conversion.

videos.headline: Meyer: That was a street fight
videos.description: Urban Meyer talks about his teams incredible OT win over Maryland and how his team never quit.

videos.headline: Haskins' 6 TD-day gives OSU win in OT thriller
videos.description: With Ohio State's playoff hopes hanging in the balance, Dwayne Haskins stops Maryland's upset bid and brings his season touchdown total to 40.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_Highlight (Haskins’ 6-TD day gives OSU win in OT thriller) 2018/11/17 ESHEET ENHL
